      "descriptionModule": {
        "briefSummary": "RENOIR Study: This study will evaluate the safety, tolerability, and efficacy of Rosnilimab in subjects with moderate to severe Rheumatoid Arthritis (RA)",
        "detailedDescription": "This study is a Phase 2 Global, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Rosnilimab in Subjects with Moderate to Severe Rheumatoid Arthritis."
      },
